<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<%- include('./_include/_head-meta.ejs', {
    title: 'WAI-ARIAのrole="alert"とsetTimeout'
}); %>
</head>

<body>
<%- include('./_include/_body-header.ejs'); %>

<main>
<h1>WAI-ARIAの<code>role="alert"</code>と<code>setTimeout</code></h1>
<span tabindex="0">ここにはタブフォーカスが当たります。６秒後にアラート文が自動的に読み上げられます。</span>
<div id="alert-div" role="alert"></div>
<script>
    setTimeout(function(){document.getElementById('alert-div').innerHTML = '<p>Hello ARIA World!（role="alert"経由）</p>';}, 6000);
</script>
</main>

<%- include('./_include/_body-footer.ejs'); %>
</body>
</html>